ide an ENTIRE play session dedicated to travel to set yourself up for the NEXT play session. (The original devs from Verant seemed to think that everyone playing this game was 15 years old, with the disposable time of a 15 year-old....)<br /><br />The old game was better in a lot of ways, true.  But it was worse in so many more.<br /><br />Treating those days of EQ as if they were the "golden days", is analagous to a widow looking back on her bastard of a dead spouse as having been a saint.</span></font></td>
